Package tp_ed.structures

Class Network<T>

java.lang.Object
tp_ed.structures.Graph<T>
tp_ed.structures.Network<T>
Type Parameters:
T - the type of elements held in this network
All Implemented Interfaces:
GraphADT<T>, NetworkADT<T>
public class Network<T> extends Graph<T> implements NetworkADT<T>
The Network class represents a network data structure, extending the functionality of a graph. It manages a set of vertices connected by edges, where each edge has an associated weight. This class also supports bidirectional edges and operations to find the shortest path and shortest path weight in the network.
